578
00:16:35,000 --> 00:16:36,360
this morning.

579
00:16:36,360 --> 00:16:38,640
I didn't respond directly
to what she said.

580
00:16:39,000 --> 00:16:41,000
I chose to pretend I didn't hear it

581
00:16:41,000 --> 00:16:41,960
or just dodge it.

582
00:16:41,960 --> 00:16:43,460
(Morning)
So, would you like someone else?

583
00:16:43,480 --> 00:16:45,360
"I chose to act like I didn't hear it".

584
00:16:45,360 --> 00:16:47,480
(Hard to judge)
Honestly, yes, but I feel

585
00:16:47,480 --> 00:16:48,340
a bit of hesitation.

586
00:16:48,360 --> 00:16:50,160
His logic is really odd.

587
00:16:50,160 --> 00:16:51,760
(Earth-shattering remark)
I was stunned.

588
00:16:51,760 --> 00:16:53,800
(Sounds weird)
It just feels off.

589
00:16:54,080 --> 00:16:55,360
Why did you jump into the water?

590
00:16:56,280 --> 00:16:57,300
Was that a show-off move?

591
00:16:57,550 --> 00:16:58,800
(Just to "show off"?)
Honestly,

592
00:16:58,800 --> 00:17:00,040
I didn't vote for Yan yesterday.

593
00:17:01,200 --> 00:17:01,880
What?

594
00:17:01,880 --> 00:17:02,520
Why tell them?

595
00:17:02,600 --> 00:17:03,340
Not a single vote.

596
00:17:03,540 --> 00:17:09,420
(Day one's affection delivery)

597
00:17:10,700 --> 00:17:12,680
(Yi Xiaofan > Zhan Jiaming 2 votes)
I'm interested

598
00:17:12,680 --> 00:17:13,320
in Miss Zhan.

599
00:17:17,440 --> 00:17:19,080
Zhan Jiaming? It's getting interesting.

600
00:17:19,080 --> 00:17:21,460
When he locked eyes with Zhan Jiaming,

601
00:17:21,460 --> 00:17:23,160
Zhan Jiaming said, "you didn't dodge me".

602
00:17:23,160 --> 00:17:24,360
Then he added,

603
00:17:24,360 --> 00:17:26,120
(A conflicted person)
"not what I expected".

604
00:17:26,320 --> 00:17:27,280
You like Jiaming,

605
00:17:27,280 --> 00:17:28,480
but the feeling you give her

606
00:17:28,480 --> 00:17:29,880
is that you like Yan.

607
00:17:30,360 --> 00:17:32,560
(Making a girl misread it)
She would be puzzled.

608
00:17:32,560 --> 00:17:33,420
We still don't get him

609
00:17:33,420 --> 00:17:34,640
(Hard-to-read)
after all this.

610
00:17:34,640 --> 00:17:36,000
(Misunderstanding)
Back and forth.

611
00:17:36,200 --> 00:17:37,040
So what about today?

612
00:17:37,720 --> 00:17:38,560
Still no clue today.

613
00:17:39,120 --> 00:17:39,860
You're mysterious.

614
00:17:40,120 --> 00:17:40,760
He is.

615
00:17:42,050 --> 00:17:43,000
That's pointless anyway.

616
00:17:43,000 --> 00:17:44,320
If there's no date planned,

617
00:17:44,800 --> 00:17:45,920
it's pointless, no go.

618
00:17:48,540 --> 00:17:49,980
(Speaking up for her on the spot)

619
00:17:50,360 --> 00:17:51,360
You're a Taurus, right?

620
00:17:51,360 --> 00:17:52,040
I'm a Taurus.

621
00:17:52,040 --> 00:17:52,840
Born in April?

622
00:17:53,080 --> 00:17:53,760
In May.

623
00:17:53,760 --> 00:17:54,640
May 3rd.

624
00:17:56,400 --> 00:17:57,520
How did you know that?

625
00:17:57,520 --> 00:17:58,800
That's an insanely good guess.

626
00:17:59,320 --> 00:17:59,800
For real?

627
00:18:00,640 --> 00:18:01,280
Seriously.

628
00:18:03,280 --> 00:18:04,440
How could you guess that?

629
00:18:04,440 --> 00:18:05,280
I thought you...

630
00:18:05,280 --> 00:18:06,400
you knew something.

631
00:18:06,400 --> 00:18:06,960
I have

632
00:18:06,960 --> 00:18:07,720
absolutely no idea.

633
00:18:08,000 --> 00:18:09,760
Then how'd you land on the 3rd?

634
00:18:10,440 --> 00:18:12,080
It just feels like the 3rd.

635
00:18:12,100 --> 00:18:13,000
You're totally in sync.

636
00:18:13,000 --> 00:18:14,860
(Such a wonderful coincidence)

637
00:18:15,240 --> 00:18:15,840
Impressive.

638
00:18:15,840 --> 00:18:16,520
So smart.

639
00:18:16,520 --> 00:18:17,760
She's seriously brilliant.

640
00:18:17,760 --> 00:18:19,200
I fall for the women in the show.

641
00:18:19,200 --> 00:18:20,100
(Won her heart)
Yeah.

642
00:18:20,120 --> 00:18:21,990
I won the game and asked you out for dinner.

643
00:18:21,990 --> 00:18:22,720
Do you like it?

644
00:18:23,920 --> 00:18:24,800
Of course I do.

645
00:18:25,280 --> 00:18:25,880
Really?

646
00:18:26,280 --> 00:18:27,120
Yeah.

647
00:18:27,400 --> 00:18:28,080
A good question.

648
00:18:28,080 --> 00:18:29,200
Is it because you get to eat?

649
00:18:29,200 --> 00:18:30,200
No, definitely not.

650
00:18:30,280 --> 00:18:31,440
It's because of you.

651
00:18:31,440 --> 00:18:32,860
(Because it's you)

652
00:18:35,440 --> 00:18:36,760
Finally, a proper meal.

653
00:18:36,760 --> 00:18:37,760
That's not the reason.

654
00:18:38,320 --> 00:18:39,120
Definitely not.

655
00:18:39,280 --> 00:18:40,400
He's getting all shy now.

656
00:18:40,580 --> 00:18:42,000
(Sweet moment alert)

657
00:18:42,000 --> 00:18:43,840
Attention, islanders.

658
00:18:43,840 --> 00:18:46,200
Affection delivery momen has begun.

659
00:18:46,200 --> 00:18:49,680
All islanders, please proceed to

660
00:18:49,680 --> 00:18:51,960
delivery your affection one by one.

661
00:18:51,960 --> 00:18:53,920
Among the male islanders tonight,

662
00:18:53,920 --> 00:18:57,680
the one with the fewest votes
will have to leave.

663
00:18:58,760 --> 00:19:00,200
Who do you all think it'll be?

664
00:19:00,200 --> 00:19:01,760
I think...

665
00:19:01,760 --> 00:19:05,600
(Ye Jiajie, Yi Xiaofan)
Ye Jiajie and Yi Xiaofan might be banished.

666
00:19:05,600 --> 00:19:06,800
I think it's Xiaofan.

667
00:19:06,960 --> 00:19:07,720
I think so too.

668
00:19:07,720 --> 00:19:09,000
My guess is Xiaofan.

669
00:19:09,000 --> 00:19:10,240
The one who got banished today

670
00:19:10,240 --> 00:19:11,320
was Ye Jiajie.

671
00:19:11,320 --> 00:19:13,440
Honestly, I think he's a good guy.

672
00:19:14,040 --> 00:19:15,280
(Hope he can stay)
Maybe it's because

673
00:19:15,280 --> 00:19:16,360
his Chinese isn't fluent,

674
00:19:16,360 --> 00:19:18,440
so he didn't talk that much.

675
00:19:19,000 --> 00:19:20,780
(Lacks communication)
He hasn't opened up to others.

676
00:19:21,160 --> 00:19:21,640
Yeah.

677
00:19:22,020 --> 00:19:22,840
(What a pity)

678
00:19:22,840 --> 00:19:23,640
I fell

679
00:19:23,640 --> 00:19:24,880
into the water today,

680
00:19:24,880 --> 00:19:26,520
every girl would think I'm into Yan.

681
00:19:26,520 --> 00:19:27,000
That means

682
00:19:27,000 --> 00:19:28,240
they probably won't vote for me.

683
00:19:29,080 --> 00:19:30,360
So if Yan doesn't vote for me,

684
00:19:30,760 --> 00:19:32,040
my vote count might end up low.

685
00:19:32,520 --> 00:19:33,120
That makes sense.

686
00:19:33,120 --> 00:19:34,360
Yanyan will vote for me,

687
00:19:36,000 --> 00:19:37,280
but the others probably won't.

688
00:19:37,520 --> 00:19:39,920
I could try to get to know Huang,

689
00:19:39,920 --> 00:19:42,360
but...

690
00:19:43,480 --> 00:19:45,040
I don't think she's that into Huang.

691
00:19:45,040 --> 00:19:47,040
Just based on their chat today.

692
00:19:47,040 --> 00:19:47,600
Yeah.

693
00:19:47,600 --> 00:19:48,360
Right?

694
00:19:48,360 --> 00:19:49,200
I think so too.

695
00:19:49,200 --> 00:19:50,800
Chen Yijia,

696
00:19:50,800 --> 00:19:54,280
please proceed to deliver your affection.

697
00:19:54,440 --> 00:19:57,000
She'll probably vote for Zizheng.

698
00:19:57,480 --> 00:19:58,000
Yeah.

699
00:19:58,100 --> 00:19:59,400
(Prediction: Chen Yijia > Zhang Zizheng)

700
00:19:59,400 --> 00:20:00,720
Will she give them all to Zizheng?

701
00:20:01,220 --> 00:20:05,540
(Chen Yijia > Zhang Zizheng, 3 weights)

702
00:20:05,560 --> 00:20:07,640
It's so wonderful
when feelings go both ways.

703
00:20:07,800 --> 00:20:09,040
Having someone to lift me up

704
00:20:09,040 --> 00:20:12,560
is actually really touching.

705
00:20:12,560 --> 00:20:13,280
So at that moment,

706
00:20:13,280 --> 00:20:14,040
I truly felt

707
00:20:14,040 --> 00:20:16,080
a completely different kind of emotion.

708
00:20:16,080 --> 00:20:17,800
This kind of guy is actually great.

709
00:20:17,800 --> 00:20:20,000
He's always aware of what she needs.

710
00:20:20,400 --> 00:20:22,240
They are such a pure love couple.

711
00:20:22,240 --> 00:20:23,000
Yeah, totally.

712
00:20:23,000 --> 00:20:24,820
(Pure Love Couple)
Feels like a campus drama.

713
00:20:24,820 --> 00:20:25,480
So sweet.

714
00:20:25,760 --> 00:20:28,840
Zhu Huiyan, please proceed to

715
00:20:28,840 --> 00:20:30,720
deliver your affection.

716
00:20:30,720 --> 00:20:32,720
I can't wait to see Yan's choice.

717
00:20:32,720 --> 00:20:33,920
(Excitement)
Me too.

718
00:20:34,320 --> 00:20:36,680
Will she choose Jiawei and…

719
00:20:36,680 --> 00:20:39,320
(Zhu Huiyan > Huang Jiawei, Yi Xiaofan)
Xiaofan.

720
00:20:39,320 --> 00:20:41,320
I don't think
she'll give it all to Jiawei.

721
00:20:41,320 --> 00:20:42,120
Yeah, I agree.

722
00:20:45,680 --> 00:20:47,120
She turns and walks away.

723
00:20:49,160 --> 00:20:49,640
Who?

724
00:20:49,640 --> 00:20:50,440
Please let us know.

725
00:20:50,440 --> 00:20:51,720
What exactly am I voting for?

726
00:20:51,840 --> 00:20:52,680
Who?

727
00:20:52,680 --> 00:20:53,680
I didn't see it.

728
00:20:54,960 --> 00:20:56,040
This is driving me nuts.

729
00:20:56,040 --> 00:20:57,480
She might have voted for someone

730
00:20:57,480 --> 00:20:58,600
totally unexpected.

731
00:20:58,700 --> 00:21:00,080
(Now that's dramatic)

732
00:21:00,080 --> 00:21:00,400
Did she

733
00:21:00,400 --> 00:21:02,760
vote for someone close with another girl?

734
00:21:02,760 --> 00:21:03,920
(Voted for a surprising man)
Well,

735
00:21:03,920 --> 00:21:04,760
it's possible.

736
00:21:05,000 --> 00:21:05,840
Could be.

737
00:21:05,840 --> 00:21:09,760
All islanders, please gather at the square.

738
00:21:09,760 --> 00:21:10,760
What do we do?

739
00:21:10,760 --> 00:21:11,840
Are you nervous?

740
00:21:11,840 --> 00:21:12,480
I'm nervous.

741
00:21:12,480 --> 00:21:13,680
We're not leaving today,

742
00:21:13,680 --> 00:21:14,680
I still feel tense.

743
00:21:15,200 --> 00:21:16,720
This game is pretty harsh.

744
00:21:17,480 --> 00:21:18,920
Someone's got to leave today.

745
00:21:22,080 --> 00:21:22,680
Tell me.

746
00:21:22,680 --> 00:21:23,580
Uneasy.

747
00:21:23,580 --> 00:21:24,480
Going public with this?

748
00:21:24,480 --> 00:21:26,200
Isn't this basically our conference room?

749
00:21:26,380 --> 00:21:28,120
(Dream Back to Offer)

750
00:21:28,120 --> 00:21:29,840
Everyone, gather in the conference room.

751
00:21:29,840 --> 00:21:31,080
Let's announce the next task.

752
00:21:31,600 --> 00:21:33,200
And see who's leaving the team.

753
00:21:33,200 --> 00:21:33,720
Right.

754
00:21:34,360 --> 00:21:37,400
Between Ye Jiajie and Yi Xiaofan,

755
00:21:38,880 --> 00:21:41,320
the one with the lower score is

756
00:21:41,320 --> 00:21:42,160
Ye Jiajie.

757
00:21:42,360 --> 00:21:43,420
He went back to the island

758
00:21:43,420 --> 00:21:44,160
and he left again.

759
00:21:44,160 --> 00:21:45,160
He barely talk now.

760
00:21:45,160 --> 00:21:46,920
I still think it might be Jie.

761
00:21:46,920 --> 00:21:48,080
He doesn't seem as close

762
00:21:48,080 --> 00:21:49,680
to anyone.

763
00:21:49,680 --> 00:21:50,880
This is tense.

764
00:21:50,880 --> 00:21:52,120
Kind of scary.

765
00:21:52,120 --> 00:21:52,740
Who could it be?

766
00:21:53,440 --> 00:21:55,600
No one actually voted
for Yi Xiaofan, right?

767
00:21:55,660 --> 00:21:57,040
(Can we even say that?)

768
00:21:57,040 --> 00:21:57,680
I think Yan

769
00:21:57,680 --> 00:21:58,680
might vote for him.

770
00:21:58,680 --> 00:22:00,040
Just a little chance.

771
00:22:00,040 --> 00:22:02,390
(Ye Jiajie would have to leave)
She might want to get to know him more.

772
00:22:02,390 --> 00:22:02,960
Right.

773
00:22:04,200 --> 00:22:04,800
Yi Xiaofan.

774
00:22:06,420 --> 00:22:08,980
(Yi Xiaofan leaves the island)

775
00:22:09,000 --> 00:22:09,780
I think it's because

776
00:22:09,780 --> 00:22:11,400
Xiaofan has been sending signals

777
00:22:11,400 --> 00:22:12,320
to different girls.

778
00:22:12,320 --> 00:22:15,360
Feels like Xiaofan might've
played the wrong strategy.

779
00:22:15,360 --> 00:22:17,000
(A strategy mistake)
But he's...

780
00:22:17,000 --> 00:22:17,740
No bad intentions.

781
00:22:17,740 --> 00:22:19,000
Just a bit of a pity.

782
00:22:19,000 --> 00:22:20,920
Maybe he picked the wrong approach.

783
00:22:20,920 --> 00:22:22,720
But honestly, I think the way he talks

784
00:22:22,720 --> 00:22:24,160
is kinda contradictory.

785
00:22:24,160 --> 00:22:26,000
(His words and actions conflict)
He said

786
00:22:26,000 --> 00:22:27,520
he didn't want others to see

787
00:22:27,520 --> 00:22:28,560
a fake version of him.

788
00:22:28,560 --> 00:22:29,840
He didn't want to put on a show.

789
00:22:29,840 --> 00:22:31,360
But a lot of the things he does...

790
00:22:31,360 --> 00:22:34,800
(A look at Yi Xiaofan's actions)
Is that really the real him?

791
00:22:36,560 --> 00:22:38,080
His life is so dramatic.

792
00:22:38,180 --> 00:22:40,340
(Too much drama to comprehend)

793
00:22:42,040 --> 00:22:43,040
It's fine, I guess.

794
00:22:45,320 --> 00:22:46,360
Here?

795
00:22:46,360 --> 00:22:46,560
Here

796
00:22:46,560 --> 00:22:46,960
is okay.

797
00:22:46,960 --> 00:22:48,120
I thought it was over there.

798
00:22:48,320 --> 00:22:48,960
Hey, man.

799
00:22:48,960 --> 00:22:50,520
What are you doing sitting here?

800
00:22:51,320 --> 00:22:52,920
They've both left already.

801
00:22:52,920 --> 00:22:54,400
At least go after them.

802
00:22:54,400 --> 00:22:55,880
Zhang Zizheng said I'm basically

803
00:22:55,880 --> 00:22:57,200
telling you what to do.

804
00:22:57,720 --> 00:22:59,480
Yeah, you need to be a little braver.

805
00:22:59,480 --> 00:23:02,000
No one's really tied to anyone right now.

806
00:23:02,000 --> 00:23:03,680
You have to fight for happiness.

807
00:23:04,220 --> 00:23:06,540
(Go for it bravely)

808
00:23:06,760 --> 00:23:08,120
(Now?)
The weather is great today.

809
00:23:08,120 --> 00:23:09,320
Like, really good.

810
00:23:09,320 --> 00:23:10,200
Hurry up.

811
00:23:10,200 --> 00:23:10,800
Go, go, go.

812
00:23:11,200 --> 00:23:12,660
Can Xuan Cheng sit between them?

813
00:23:12,660 --> 00:23:15,040
(Backing him to sit in the middle)

814
00:23:15,040 --> 00:23:16,280
He went back to his room.

815
00:23:18,720 --> 00:23:19,680
He's looking for them.

816
00:23:21,400 --> 00:23:22,960
Tomorrow I'm just going to have fun.

817
00:23:23,760 --> 00:23:25,360
If I get eliminated tomorrow...

818
00:23:25,360 --> 00:23:26,620
No way.

819
00:23:26,620 --> 00:23:27,120
Impossible.

820
00:23:27,120 --> 00:23:28,080
I won't let that happen.

821
00:23:28,080 --> 00:23:28,920
Trust me on this.

822
00:23:34,640 --> 00:23:36,120
This is just heartbreaking.

823
00:23:36,840 --> 00:23:38,120
Ouch, that hurts.

824
00:23:38,120 --> 00:23:38,960
He's about to have

825
00:23:38,960 --> 00:23:40,680
the inspiration to write a song.

826
00:23:40,740 --> 00:23:41,640
(Got the inspiration)

827
00:23:41,640 --> 00:23:44,000
He'll write a love ballad right away.

828
00:23:44,480 --> 00:23:46,440
He's just waiting for the right moment.

829
00:23:46,440 --> 00:23:47,040
I think.

830
00:23:47,040 --> 00:23:47,480
Yeah.

831
00:23:50,200 --> 00:23:51,720
Leave the dishes to me.

832
00:23:51,720 --> 00:23:53,040
Turning frustration into the urge.

833
00:23:53,040 --> 00:23:54,320
If you want to wash, you wash.

834
00:23:54,320 --> 00:23:55,000
I'll wash.

835
00:23:55,520 --> 00:23:56,360
Is it now...

836
00:23:56,760 --> 00:23:57,320
Nobody move.

837
00:23:57,320 --> 00:23:58,160
Let me handle it.

838
00:23:58,720 --> 00:23:59,760
I think his behavior

839
00:23:59,760 --> 00:24:00,560
feels a bit boyish.

840
00:24:00,560 --> 00:24:00,800
Yeah.

841
00:24:00,800 --> 00:24:01,480
Same feeling.

842
00:24:01,480 --> 00:24:02,080
It's a bit...

843
00:24:02,400 --> 00:24:03,200
Unreasonable.

844
00:24:03,200 --> 00:24:03,680
Yeah.

845
00:24:03,680 --> 00:24:04,120
Totally.

846
00:24:04,600 --> 00:24:06,880
Sulking, but not sure at who.

847
00:24:06,880 --> 00:24:08,480
(The bowl took the blame)
At the bowl.

848
00:24:08,480 --> 00:24:10,040
Do we still need to wash this bowl?

849
00:24:10,520 --> 00:24:11,320
You wanna wash it?

850
00:24:11,480 --> 00:24:11,720
Sure.

851
00:24:11,720 --> 00:24:12,520
I'll do it.

852
00:24:12,520 --> 00:24:13,080
A new chance.

853
00:24:13,080 --> 00:24:13,880
Let me wash it then.

854
00:24:13,880 --> 00:24:14,180
Let me.

855
00:24:14,180 --> 00:24:14,960
I have time anyway.

856
00:24:14,960 --> 00:24:16,920
Hurry.

857
00:24:16,920 --> 00:24:18,160
(Impatient)
What's going on?

858
00:24:18,160 --> 00:24:18,720
I'll wash it.

